---
title: Grilled Sea Bass With Creamy Tomato Pasta
description: .
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/grilled-sea-bass-1ba7d845-ac17a759.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/grilled-sea-bass-5fc8ca5cab85df7dca5ab94b-9fb6dcb2.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/grilled-sea-bass-5fc8ca5cab85df7dca5ab94b
servings: 2
author: Michael Steadman
time required: 10 minutes
course: main course
cuisine: European
